{"tid":1362960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"木奠鬼拍後尾枕－執法人員，施暴人員？？？","createTime":"2019-07-25T04:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T04:40:28.000Z","uid":269027,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61ef83254bf161a6b38e31a40830061a5d90cc6b","tid":1362960,"uid":269027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:35:12.000Z","msg":"林鄭在元朗白衣兇徒恐襲式無差別打市民事件之後記者會，有一段令我毛管戙。<br />\n去片飛到大約24分鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/22291/元朗打人-林鄭月娥-盧偉聰-22291/林鄭月娥\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F22291%2F%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%89%93%E4%BA%BA-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E8%81%B0-22291%2F%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=4b8bb9fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/22291/元朗打人-林鄭月娥-盧偉聰-22291/林鄭月娥</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭：「我哋一定唔會容忍任何暴力...唔會將執法人員同施暴人員擺埋一齊...」<br />\n<br />\n我有無聽錯？<br />\n<br />\n見人無差別咁亂打嘅唔係叫暴徒咩？乜嘢叫 「施暴人員」？？？？<br />\n<br />\n即係成件事係有劇本和角色：執法人員，施暴人員<br />\n真係冇「擺埋一齊」️，「施暴人員」做完佢哋角色，警方唔出場住，待「施暴人員」完成任務收隊，警方出場。呢樣叫鬼拍後尾枕。<br />\n<br />\n我睇直播去到呢個位即刻要熄電視。"},{"pid":"fd1daa4cf9f28bf527112efa00f6336ff14e41d9","tid":1362960,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n武力要升級 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣都要升級</span></span><br />\n(呼籲!!)(汲取G20經驗)關於登報一事提升輿論問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360136</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b44c6772b71b736525e8ecafdd95ed7b3905513","tid":1362960,"uid":147661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:40:28.000Z","msg":"前腳黎 後腳走 <br />\n<br />\n咪冇放埋一齊<br />